  amd64 stable, bug #261108

  06 Mar 2009; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> pam-1.0.4.ebuild:
  alpha/arm/ia64/s390/sh/x86 stable wrt #261108

  05 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> pam-1.0.4.ebuild:
